cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with text classification. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses Reinforcement Learning for learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with document classification. Finally, it could also belong to cs.SD (Software Engineering) as it proposes a new algorithm for text classification.
